365
00:27:12,541 --> 00:27:16,291
Tidak, kami masih di luar.
Tapi bagaimana keadaan Blue?

366
00:27:16,375 --> 00:27:18,166
- Blue baik.
- Hadirin,

367
00:27:18,250 --> 00:27:20,166
