00:27:45,958 --> 00:27:48,500
Ibu ingin tahu
apa kau makan malam di rumah.

377
00:27:49,958 --> 00:27:52,083
Kurasa tak sempat. Aku akan pulang larut.

378
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:55,916
